parameters: It's Int'oma's most dangerous place, and
there's no end to the number of criminals
I read about the information of this city
well in advance. In it, the place named
"Decadent Street" is the one place where
we should never enter at any cost.
S-since when... where'd you read that?
While I was waiting to get my certificate,
I took a peek at the brochures.
So── is this trick of posing as a guide
your way of luring us into this place?
How amusing your little trip was.
You let us all the way west, without even
HOW TROUBLESOME... YOU CAME ALL THIS WAY,
SO JUST BECOME MY FOOD ALREADY.
to lure us to this street.
That the guide was a trap!
You left me looking like a fool all on my own!
Well, um... you seemed like you were having fun,
so I didn't want to intrude...
So you thought I was stupid, huh!?
...I'm sorry. I didn't think you'd feel that way.
I couldn't consider your feelings, Fiede.
I don't like being called an idiot, but...
It doesn't sit right with me.
...Hey, how about we go sightseeing again?
C'mon, I'll go out with you.
